content: Here's what I bought this month: a few camisoles from H&M, a pair of ankle boots from Zara, a set of notecards from The Paperie, a custom planner from Etsy, an eyeshadow palette from Sephora, and a few travel-sized skincare products from Drunk Elephant. Also, I bought two pairs of jeans from Levi's at Macy's - no price is mentioned for the jeans, but we need this fact to know that two pairs were bought.
